tafsir[7]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Because of the habit of the Quraysh and their acquaintance."
  107,1,"Do you recognise the one who rejects the requital on the Day of Judgement?"
  107,2,"It is the one who harshly turns away the orphan when in need."
  107,3,"He does not encourage himself nor others in feeding the poor."
  107,4,"So destruction and punishment be upon those who perform prayer."
  107,5,"Those who are heedless of their prayer; they do not care about it such that its time expires."
  107,7,"And they refrain from helping others with things in which there is no difficulty helping in."